42:["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-4 text-sm leading-7 text-zinc-300","children":"Surat PORTADOR Network is a time-critical logistics solution for cargo that cannot wait for routine courier cycles. PORTADOR SOS plans the movement around airport access, direct air cargo coordination where feasible, documentation readiness, and a human operations desk watching the deadline."}]
